description.displayText: Amazing babysitter, gave us all the time we needed. Helped around the house without being asked. She was excellent with all of our kids, i really love Nube and so do my kids, I've recommended her to many of my family members and friends.

description.displayText: We interviewed Nube and liked her very much because she was very sweet, has experience and seem to love kids very much. We were very honest about what we needed in terms of hours and schedule and according to her there were no problems so we decided to hire her. She was going to start with me a few days before I started work. She showed up the first day and on the second day never showed up or even bothered calling or texting. I had to text her!!! She replied that she was sorry but just couldn't work with us because of family issues with her kids. This is completely unacceptable since she gave us her word and we stopped looking for a nanny. If she knew it wasn't going to work, she should've call or be honest not just NOT SHOW UP.
